    {
      "id": 10788,
      "category": "team",
      "content": "Due to the lack of sanitisation in the commend area, with a especially crafted message, is possible to execute a XSS with the \"preview\" function. If a draft is save, is possible to exploit this bug using as and stored-XSS.",
